 The nurse who juggles being a mother a nurse and aspiring star shared that her matron hates her because of controversial alter-ego Skolopad.Speaking to TshisaLIVE Skolopad s manager Tebogo Mofokeng said they were dealing with the matter internally and would revert as soon as there was something to share. He added that the little outburst on social media by Skolopad was probably emotional I m trying to resolve work place issues internally and will revert to you on Monday as soon as I have something concrete to share. As for the tweets it was just fuelled by emotions he said.Skolopad said in her tweets that she wished her matron knew why she had to have her music persona. She also claimed that her plans for Durban July are being sabotaged .The musician is a nurse at a hospital in Bethlehem. 